f these are the same as `success()`:\n\n- win\n- good\n- ok\n- successful\n\nAll of these are the same as `failure()`:\n\n- fail\n- bad\n- error\n","maintainers":[{"name":"markhuge","email":"mark@segfawlt.net"}],"time":{"modified":"2014-11-12T04:00:55.360Z","created":"2014-11-12T04:00:55.360Z","0.1.0":"2014-11-12T04:00:55.360Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/markhuge/posicon-hipchat","keywords":["hipchat","posicon","emoticon","hubot"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/markhuge/posicon-hipchat.git"},"author":{"name":"Mark Wilkerson","email":"mark@segfalwt.net"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/markhuge/posicon-hipchat/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"README.md"}
